# CLIP ChangeLog for sys-fs/cryptsetup

*cryptsetup-1.6.5-r1 (12 Jan 2016)

  12 Jan 2016; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +cryptsetup-1.6.5-r1.ebuild, -cryptsetup-1.6.5.ebuild:
  Restore /bin/cryptsetup symlink that was left out in last 
  commit - we still have that path hardcoded in at least userd.

*cryptsetup-1.6.5 (30 Dec 2015)

  30 Dec 2015; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +cryptsetup-1.6.5.ebuild, -cryptsetup-1.6.2-r1.ebuild,
  +files/1.5.1-dmcrypt.rc, -files/dmcrypt.rc:
  Bump to latest stable.

*cryptsetup-1.6.2-r1 (29 Dec 2015)

  29 Dec 2015; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +cryptsetup-1.6.2-r1.ebuild, -cryptsetup-1.6.2.ebuild:
  Force rebuild, libgcrypt revdep.

*cryptsetup-1.6.2 (19 Mar 2014)

  19 Mar 2014; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +cryptsetup-1.6.2.ebuild, -cryptsetup-1.4.3.ebuild,
