*cryptsetup-1.4.3 (19 Aug 2013)

  19 Aug 2013; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +cryptsetup-1.4.3.ebuild, -cryptsetup-1.1.3-r4.ebuild,
  -files/1.0.5-dm-crypt-start.sh, -files/1.0.5-dm-crypt-stop.sh,
