  -files/1.1.3-dm-crypt-start.sh, -files/1.1.3-dm-crypt-stop.sh,
  +files/dmcrypt.rc:
  Bump to latest.

  24 Dec 2012; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  cryptsetup-1.1.3-r4.ebuild:
  Simplify build depends for !dynamic.

  20 Dec 2012; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  cryptsetup-1.1.3-r4.ebuild, -cryptsetup-1.1.3-r2.ebuild:
  Re-add missing pkg_predeb() and sbindir. Remove old.
  Add dependency on util-linux[static-libs] for static builds.

*cryptsetup-1.1.3-r4 (20 Dec 2012)

  20 Dec 2012; Yves-Alexis Perez <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +cryptsetup-1.1.3-r4.ebuild, -cryptsetup-1.1.3-r3.ebuild:
  Integrate CLIP-specific modifications.

  09 Jul 2012; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  cryptsetup-1.1.3-r2.ebuild:
  Add dependency on util-linux[static-libs] when building a
  static cryptsetup - needed for liuuid.a.

