*cryptsetup-luks-1.0.3-r3 (28 Mar 2008)

  28 Mar 2008; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +cryptsetup-luks-1.0.3-r3.ebuild, -cryptsetup-luks-1.0.3-r2.ebuild:
  Change the forced capabilities into authorized ones, activated by the
  inheritable mask of e.g. xdm.
 
  12 Jan 2006; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  cryptsetup-luks-1.0.3-r2.ebuild:
  Add verictl support, grant cryptsetup the following possible caps :
   - CAP_SYS_ADMIN
   - CAP_MKNOD
  

